dct_description_sm: Includes text and key map. Sheets 75, 96, and 115-124 of Elizabeth, N.J. series; sheets 119-124 show Hillside Township, with key map. Sheets 75 and 96 headed: New sheet, Apr. 1918; sheets 115-124 headed: Add'l. sheet, Apr. 1918.
